{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:0","text":"允许通过 pattern graphs（图案图）传递 GPrim primitive variables（primvars）。可用它代替"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:1","text":"PxrPrimvar"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:2","text":"Input Parameters"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:3","text":"Variable Name"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:4","text":"primitive variable（primvar）的名称。如果未选择任何项，应在 UI 中填写 \"PrimVar\" 字段来指定自己的选择。"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:5","text":"可包含以下选项："}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:6","text":"着色位置 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:7","text":"未置换位置 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:8","text":"着色法线 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:9","text":"几何法线 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:10","text":"未置换法线 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:11","text":"着色切线 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:12","text":"归一化视图向量 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:13","text":"视图向量长度 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:14","text":"表面平均曲率 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:15","text":"表面 U 方向曲率 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:16","text":"表面 V 方向曲率 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:17","text":"Ray Spread（光线扩散） ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:18","text":"光线半径 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:19","text":"微多边形半径 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:20","text":"微多边形尺寸 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:21","text":"反射偏置 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:22","text":"透射 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:23","text":"表面 U ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:24","text":"表面 V ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:25","text":"表面 W ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:26","text":"表面 UV ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:27","text":"表面 UVW ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:28","text":"光线 footprint U ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:29","text":"光线 footprint V ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:30","text":"光线 footprint W ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:31","text":"光线 footprint UV ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:32","text":"光线 footprint UVW ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:33","text":"表面导数 U ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:34","text":"表面导数 V ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:35","text":"表面导数 W ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:36","text":"速度 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:37","text":"时间 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:38","text":"外部 IOR ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:39","text":"不透明度 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:40","text":"前向运动 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:41","text":"后向运动 ("}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:42","text":"PrimVar"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:43","text":"添加 primitive variable（primvar）的名称"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:44","text":"Type"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:45","text":"primitive variable（primvar）的类型；这必须与你作为 Variable 选择的类型匹配："}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:46","text":"float"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:47","text":"float2"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:48","text":"color"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:49","text":"point"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:50","text":"vector"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:51","text":"normal"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:52","text":"Coordinate System"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:53","text":"默认情况下，shader 使用当前坐标系。可用的坐标系包括"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:54","text":"world"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:55","text":"object"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:56","text":"，或"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:57","text":"user-defined"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:58","text":"坐标系。"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:59","text":"Output Parameters"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:60","text":"result RGB"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:61","text":"以 color 形式输出的结果。"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:62","text":"result F"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:63","text":"以 float 形式输出的结果。"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:64","text":"result F3"}
{"item_id":"a17c5c2325:65","text":"以三个 float 形式输出的结果。"}
